@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cknfpy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(v2) + tmp)
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.16 * v2 + 0.63) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.74)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.33)) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.74) / (tmp + 0.04 + v2 + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
